#: data/functions.xml.in:667
msgid "r:hyperfactorial"
msgstr "hyperfakultet"

#: data/functions.xml.in:669
msgid ""
"Calculates the hyperfactorial of an integer. Multiplies the argument raised "
"by itself with every lesser positive integer raised by themselves (1^1 * "
"2^2 ... n^n)."
msgstr ""
"Beräknar hyperfakulteten för ett heltal. Multiplicerar parametern upphöjt "
"med varje mindre positivt heltal upphöjt dem själva(1^1 * 2^2 ... n^n)."

#: data/functions.xml.in:677
