#: data/functions.xml.in:1869
msgid ""
"Reads a number in a IEEE 754 floating-point format. The number will be read "
"as a binary number, unless it contains digits other than 1 or 0. If the "
"third argument (exponent bits) is set to zero, the standard number of "
"exponent bits will be used (e.g. 8 for 32-bit format)."
msgstr ""
"Läser ett tal i ett format IEEE 754-flyttal. Talet tolkas som ett binärt, "
"såvida det inte innehåller andra siffror än 1 eller 0  Om den tredje "
"parametern (exponentbitar) anges som noll, används standardantal "
"exponentbitar (t.ex. 8 för format med 32 bitar)"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1871
msgid "Floating-point number (binary)"
msgstr "Flyttal (binärt)"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1874 data/functions.xml.in:1891
#: data/functions.xml.in:1908 data/functions.xml.in:1925
#: data/functions.xml.in:1942
msgid "Number of bits"
msgstr "Antal bitar"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1877 data/functions.xml.in:1894
#: data/functions.xml.in:1911 data/functions.xml.in:1928
#: data/functions.xml.in:1945
msgid "Number of exponent bits"
msgstr "Antal exponentbitar"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1880 data/functions.xml.in:1897
#: data/functions.xml.in:1914 data/functions.xml.in:1931
#: data/functions.xml.in:1948
msgid "Position of sign bit"
msgstr "Position för teckenbit"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1884
msgid "IEEE 754 Floating-Point Bits"
msgstr "IEEE 754-flyttal: bitar"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1885
msgid "r:floatBits"
msgstr "-"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1886
msgid ""
"Converts a value to a number in a IEEE 754 floating-point format and returns "
"the number corresponding to the binary representation. If the third argument "
"(exponent bits) is set to zero, the standard number of exponent bits will be "
"used (e.g. 8 for 32-bit format)."
msgstr ""
"Omvandlar ett värde till ett tal i ett format IEEE 754-flyttal och "
"returnerar ett tal som motsvarar den binära representation. Om den tredje "
"parametern (exponentbitar) anges som noll, används standardantal "
"exponentbitar (t.ex. 8 för format med 32 bitar)"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1901
msgid "IEEE 754 Floating-Point Error"
msgstr "IEEE 754-flyttal: omvandlingsfel"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1902
msgid "r:floatError"
msgstr "-"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1903
msgid ""
"Calculates the error (the difference between the original and the converted "
"value) when converting a value to a IEEE 754 floating-point format. If the "
"third argument (exponent bits) is set to zero, the standard number of "
"exponent bits will be used (e.g. 8 for 32-bit format)."
msgstr ""
"Beräknar felvärdet (skillnaden mellan ursprungligt och omvandlat värde) vid "
"omvandling ett tal i ett IEEE 754-flyttal. Om den tredje parametern "
"(exponentbitar) anges som noll, används standardantal exponentbitar (t.ex. 8 "
"för format med 32 bitar)"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1918
msgid "IEEE 754 Floating-Point Components"
msgstr "IEEE 754-flyttal: komponenter"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1919
msgid "r:floatParts"
msgstr "-"

#: data/functions.xml.in:1920
msgid ""
"Converts a value to a number in a IEEE 754 floating-point format and returns "
"sign, exponent, and significand in a vector. If the third argument (exponent "
"bits) is set to zero, the standard number of exponent bits will be used "
"(e.g. 8 for 32-bit format)."
msgstr ""
"Omvandlar ett värde till ett tal i ett format för IEEE 754-flyttal och "
"returnerar tecken, exponent och signifikand i en vektor. Om den tredje "
"parametern (exponentbitar) anges som noll, används standardantal "
